{"title":"吕家庄优良品种出了名（图片）","authors":["彭彬","任迁乔","彭翰春"],"dates":[{"year":1952,"month":3,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕家庄优良品种出了名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭彬  任迁乔  彭翰春  作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）山东莒县吕家庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种地的老法没变样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府号召要选种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说：“老辈没选种，一样能打粮。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）共产党员带头干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首先动手来试验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深耕细作多加工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好种籽准有好收成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）新办法实在强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果真不错多打粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开了个会和大家讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少都夸奖。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}